<c.bg_transparent>and the armory until further notice.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:52.763 --> 00:07:54.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you expecting an attack, sir?</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:54.599 --> 00:07:57.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Around here, you never know.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:59.395 --> 00:08:01.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll see you both in the morning.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:04.150 --> 00:08:07.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs ) Isn't it about feeding time?</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:07.153 --> 00:08:09.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll take care of it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after I get you settled.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:09.363 --> 00:08:12.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would you mind? I'm really not that tired.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:12.116 --> 00:08:13.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be my guest.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:13.451 --> 00:08:16.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Vulcan root leaf's in that container.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:20.791 --> 00:08:22.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's strange.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:24.712 --> 00:08:26.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's...</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:08:27.882 --> 00:08:32.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the alien communicates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with me, it's...</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:32.637 --> 00:08:34.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's almost like he's inside my head,</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:08:34.805 --> 00:08:37.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>looking at things through my eyes,</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:08:37.725 --> 00:08:40.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>experiencing what I'm experiencing.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:08:42.104 --> 00:08:44.774 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And talking to him is...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is like talking to myself.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:08:44.857 --> 00:08:46.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Does that make any sense?</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:08:46.609 --> 00:08:48.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It makes perfect sense.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:49.654 --> 00:08:52.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Listening to your thoughts</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has been very pleasurable.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:52.365 --> 00:08:53.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:53.824 --> 00:08:56.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been with you for several days...</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:56.410 --> 00:09:01.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>studying your mind, your memories,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>learning so many things about you.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:09:01.791 --> 00:09:03.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why me?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:09:03.251 --> 00:09:06.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My telepathy only works in rare instances.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:09:06.504 --> 00:09:09.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It takes a unique mind to process it.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:09:09.131 --> 00:09:12.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yours is the first I've found</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in many years.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:09:13.010 --> 00:09:14.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:09:16.347 --> 00:09:18.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm only three light-years away.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:09:19.016 --> 00:09:21.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My home is what you're seeing right now.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:09:21.769 --> 00:09:24.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All I want is to meet you.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:09:24.647 --> 00:09:26.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think that'll be possible.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:09:26.941 --> 00:09:29.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know you're on an urgent mission.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:09:29.443 --> 00:09:31.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's what I want to talk to you about.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:09:33.739 --> 00:09:35.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What did he tell you about the Xindi?</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:09:35.533 --> 00:09:37.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's saving that for my visit.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:09:39.954 --> 00:09:43.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He could have given you something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as a show of good faith.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:09:43.624 --> 00:09:46.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This could be another attempt by the Xindi</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to infiltrate </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

145
00:09:46.877 --> 00:09:48.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think he wants to help.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:09:48.629 --> 00:09:50.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was horrified that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>seven million of us were killed.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:09:50.923 --> 00:09:55.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He says he's willing to use his abilities</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to help us find the Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:55.177 --> 00:09:57.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think that's reason enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to meet with him.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:10:04.103 --> 00:10:05.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:10:05.313 --> 00:10:06.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Archer to Mayweather.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:10:06.522 --> 00:10:07.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAYWEATHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Go ahead, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

152
00:10:11.402 --> 00:10:13.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're taking a slight detour.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:10:43.851 --> 00:10:45.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( wind rushing )</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:09.794 --> 00:11:11.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( doors creak shut )</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:15.424 --> 00:11:17.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( doors creak )</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:23.724 --> 00:11:26.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: I asked Hoshi to come alone.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:11:29.146 --> 00:11:32.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Captain's always a part</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of first contact missions...</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:11:32.733 --> 00:11:34.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Starfleet regulations.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:11:34.777 --> 00:11:36.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope that's not a problem.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:36.946 --> 00:11:39.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:39.281 --> 00:11:42.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm pleased all three of you could come.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:51.669 --> 00:11:54.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My name is Tarquin.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:11:54.922 --> 00:11:58.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm obviously not what you expected.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:11:58.801 --> 00:12:00.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't want to frighten you,</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:12:00.761 --> 00:12:04.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so I created a human image</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when I contacted you on </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

166
00:12:05.266 --> 00:12:08.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you for coming to me.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:12:08.227 --> 00:12:10.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said you could help us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with our mission.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:12:11.355 --> 00:12:15.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're searching for a weapon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that could annihilate your planet.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:12:15.151 --> 00:12:17.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I may be able to find it.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:12:17.570 --> 00:12:20.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I'll need an object</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's associated with the Xindi.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:12:20.698 --> 00:12:21.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:12:21.907 --> 00:12:27.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every artifact retains an imprint</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the people who made it, who used it.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:12:28.038 --> 00:12:30.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have the ability to sense</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>those imprints.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:12:31.333 --> 00:12:34.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could arrange</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to have something sent down.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:12:34.128 --> 00:12:36.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How much time would you need with it?</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:12:36.297 --> 00:12:37.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No more than a few days.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:12:38.466 --> 00:12:40.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We didn't pick up any other bio-signs.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:12:40.426 --> 00:12:41.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take it you live here alone.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:12:43.804 --> 00:12:45.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alone.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:12:45.139 --> 00:12:47.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's an awfully big planet for one person.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:12:48.350 --> 00:12:52.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've lived here for a very long time,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. Reed.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:12:52.855 --> 00:12:56.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My only contact with the outside world</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has been through telepathy.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:12:58.360 --> 00:13:01.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring me the artifact.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'd like to get started.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:13:02.990 --> 00:13:05.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be back as soon as we can.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:13:05.201 --> 00:13:08.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain... One small request.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:13:09.997 --> 00:13:12.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd like Hoshi to stay with me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>while I'm working.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:13:15.586 --> 00:13:17.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid that's not appropriate.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:13:17.630 --> 00:13:21.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nonetheless,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's a condition of my helping you.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:13:27.348 --> 00:13:29.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I'm comfortable with this...</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:13:31.685 --> 00:13:33.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't get the sense</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that he would harm me.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:13:33.812 --> 00:13:37.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My instincts tell me otherwise.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's hiding something.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:13:37.483 --> 00:13:41.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If he's insistent,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we could put off looking for the sphere,</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:41.320 --> 00:13:42.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>stay in orbit.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:42.488 --> 00:13:43.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's only for a few days.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:43.656 --> 00:13:45.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't have the luxury</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:45.157 --> 00:13:48.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of dealing with one problem</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at a time anymore, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:13:48.202 --> 00:13:50.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If he can tell us something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the Xindi weapon,</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:13:50.663 --> 00:13:52.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it's worth the risk.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:13:54.833 --> 00:13:57.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can take care of myself, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:14:04.385 --> 00:14:07.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is from the weapon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that attacked your planet.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:14:07.555 --> 00:14:11.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We think it was a prototype...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from a much larger weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:14:11.850 --> 00:14:14.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This will be very useful.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:14:14.562 --> 00:14:15.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I?</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:14:16.605 --> 00:14:17.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:14:21.443 --> 00:14:22.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I need a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:14:22.778 --> 00:14:25.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( breathes deeply ) Take your time.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:14:29.827 --> 00:14:31.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do I have to tell you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to stay on your toes?</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:14:31.787 --> 00:14:33.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( door closes )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I think that falls</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:14:33.539 --> 00:14:35.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>under the "goes without saying"</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>category, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:14:37.001 --> 00:14:38.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did you bring a phase-pistol?</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:14:38.919 --> 00:14:40.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll keep it under my pillow.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:14:44.925 --> 00:14:46.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know how to reach me.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:14:47.261 --> 00:14:48.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( footsteps receding )</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:15:01.817 --> 00:15:04.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you always eat like this?</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:15:04.445 --> 00:15:06.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only when I have company.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:15:09.992 --> 00:15:11.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:15:11.660 --> 00:15:15.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought you might enjoy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something familiar.</c.bg_transparent>

218
