327
00:21:53.020 --> 00:21:54.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aren't you supposed to know me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>better than that?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:21:55.063 --> 00:21:57.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles ) What did you think of it?</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:21:59.026 --> 00:22:03.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's an interesting language...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>reminds me of medieval Klingon.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:22:04.281 --> 00:22:05.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Any progress?</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:22:05.949 --> 00:22:09.745 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A few images, impressions.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:22:09.828 --> 00:22:12.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did you know that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there are five Xindi species?</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:22:12.789 --> 00:22:14.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's what we've heard.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:22:14.249 --> 00:22:16.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A great deal of conflict among them.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:22:16.543 --> 00:22:18.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They don't trust one another.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:22:18.337 --> 00:22:20.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you know where</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they're building the weapon?</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:22:21.673 --> 00:22:24.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not yet. I'm going to need more time.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:22:27.679 --> 00:22:28.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's this?</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:22:31.099 --> 00:22:34.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It helps me extend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the range of my telepathy.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:22:34.186 --> 00:22:36.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My family gave it to me when I was exiled.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:22:37.481 --> 00:22:40.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Without it, I never would have found you.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:22:44.154 --> 00:22:45.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Would you like to try?</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:22:46.031 --> 00:22:47.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that possible?</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:22:47.991 --> 00:22:49.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>With guidance.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:23:06.593 --> 00:23:11.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you close your eyes,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll begin to sense light and color.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:23:12.182 --> 00:23:18.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let the images take shape,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and let the shapes become more distinct.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:23:19.064 --> 00:23:23.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Can you see them?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I think so.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:23:23.819 --> 00:23:26.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're trying too hard to find them.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:23:27.030 --> 00:23:29.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let the images come to you.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:23:56.560 --> 00:23:58.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you make sense of all that?</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:23:58.520 --> 00:24:01.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It takes practice. Try again.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:24:04.943 --> 00:24:06.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe later.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:24:06.987 --> 00:24:09.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I should let you get back to your work.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:24:11.950 --> 00:24:16.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, feel free to return...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If you'd like some company.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:24:16.997 --> 00:24:18.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:24:59.998 --> 00:25:02.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( wind rushing )</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:25:14.554 --> 00:25:17.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I asked you to stay inside!</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:25:17.474 --> 00:25:19.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is this why you didn't want me out here?</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:25:19.976 --> 00:25:21.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who are they?</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:25:21.228 --> 00:25:22.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're people I knew.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:25:22.520 --> 00:25:25.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The last one died over a century ago.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:25:25.148 --> 00:25:26.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should go inside.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:25:26.233 --> 00:25:27.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did they die?</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:25:27.859 --> 00:25:32.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very few lifespans are as long as mine.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:25:32.113 --> 00:25:33.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How old are you?</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:25:33.406 --> 00:25:36.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was born over 400 years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:25:36.952 --> 00:25:38.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who were they?</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:25:38.995 --> 00:25:41.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The first one was Morianna Taal.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:25:43.041 --> 00:25:45.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She was my first companion.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:25:45.752 --> 00:25:49.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like you, she had a unique mind.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:25:51.007 --> 00:25:52.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the other three?</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:25:52.509 --> 00:25:54.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Companions as well.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:25:54.844 --> 00:25:56.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I lost Morianna,</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:25:56.388 --> 00:26:00.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I-I began to search for another...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And another.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:26:00.684 --> 00:26:02.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:26:02.435 --> 00:26:05.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sometimes, I don't know what is worse...</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:26:05.397 --> 00:26:10.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>being alone or having to bury the people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've come to care about.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:26:10.485 --> 00:26:13.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's been many years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>since I found someone like you.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:26:13.947 --> 00:26:16.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're right. We should go back inside.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:26:16.408 --> 00:26:19.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All I'm asking is that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you consider the possibility.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:26:19.577 --> 00:26:22.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know that </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is on an important mission.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:26:22.247 --> 00:26:24.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just can't abandon my duties.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:26:24.457 --> 00:26:27.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's possible that, with my help,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your mission will be over soon.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:26:27.752 --> 00:26:30.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you really expect me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to spend the rest of my life</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:26:30.547 --> 00:26:31.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a desolate world</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:26:31.965 --> 00:26:34.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>with someone that I have known</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for less than two days?</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:26:34.801 --> 00:26:36.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The others had similar doubts.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:26:36.303 --> 00:26:37.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But over time,</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:26:37.846 --> 00:26:40.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they came to appreciate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what I had to offer them.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:26:40.640 --> 00:26:44.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one will ever understand you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the way I can.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:26:44.561 --> 00:26:46.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am grateful for your help,</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:26:46.146 --> 00:26:48.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm happy to stay here while you work,</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:26:48.189 --> 00:26:51.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I have no intention</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of becoming your next companion.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:26:59.034 --> 00:27:01.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( breathing deeply )</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:27:01.995 --> 00:27:03.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you think projecting yourself as human</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:27:04.080 --> 00:27:06.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>is going to make me change my mind,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're mistaken.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:27:06.875 --> 00:27:10.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've let your fear of the unknown</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>stand in your way far too many times.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:27:10.545 --> 00:27:12.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You almost left </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>early in its mission</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:27:12.797 --> 00:27:15.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because you didn't think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you could control your fears.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:27:15.300 --> 00:27:17.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But in spite of that, you stayed.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:27:17.844 --> 00:27:19.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It strengthened you.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:27:19.929 --> 00:27:22.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This situation is no different.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:27:22.849 --> 00:27:25.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You obviously misinterpreted</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a few memories,</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:27:25.894 --> 00:27:28.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>because this situation is very different.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:27:28.229 --> 00:27:29.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm giving you the chance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to experience something</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:27:30.023 --> 00:27:32.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you've searched for your entire life.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:27:32.567 --> 00:27:37.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the reason you study languages,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to make unique connections with people.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:27:37.364 --> 00:27:40.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't need you to help me do that.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:27:40.283 --> 00:27:43.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why do you seem so isolated?</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:27:43.703 --> 00:27:46.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You live on a ship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>filled with your own people,</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:27:47.040 --> 00:27:50.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and yet there are many times</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when you feel alone.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:27:50.877 --> 00:27:52.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stay with me.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:27:53.046 --> 00:27:58.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll teach you ways of sharing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>thoughts and emotions no human can.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:28:00.428 --> 00:28:03.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I already told you, I'm not interested.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:28:03.681 --> 00:28:05.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're lying, Hoshi.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:28:05.975 --> 00:28:08.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can hear everything you're thinking.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:28:08.603 --> 00:28:10.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What I'm thinking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is none of your business!</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:28:11.064 --> 00:28:12.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Michio.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:28:13.691 --> 00:28:15.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your grandfather...</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:28:15.693 --> 00:28:18.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's the last person</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you were truly close to.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:28:18.696 --> 00:28:20.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But he died a long time ago.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:28:20.990 --> 00:28:22.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leave me alone.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:28:22.242 --> 00:28:24.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that kind of connection again.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:28:24.619 --> 00:28:26.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leave me alone!</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:28:27.831 --> 00:28:29.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:28:29.249 --> 00:28:32.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know this must seem overwhelming.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:28:32.710 --> 00:28:34.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think about what I've said.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:28:34.754 --> 00:28:36.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're going to have a great deal of time.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:28:50.145 --> 00:28:51.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:28:51.354 --> 00:28:55.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sensors say we're passing through</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a gravimetric distortion.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:28:55.400 --> 00:28:57.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:29:00.447 --> 00:29:02.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No anomalies.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:29:02.949 --> 00:29:05.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trellium seems to be doing its job.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:29:05.785 --> 00:29:08.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Archer to </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

435
00:29:08.204 --> 00:29:09.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Go ahead.</i></c.bg_transparent>

436
00:29:09.873 --> 00:29:13.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're approaching 79,000 kilometers.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:29:13.877 --> 00:29:16.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Still no sign of the cloaking barrier.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:29:16.171 --> 00:29:19.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Adjust your heading to 016 mark 2.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:29:19.883 --> 00:29:20.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

440
00:29:26.264 --> 00:29:27.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:29:27.557 --> 00:29:29.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:29:30.059 --> 00:29:32.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That felt promising.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:29:32.437 --> 00:29:34.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe you just grazed the perimeter.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:29:34.564 --> 00:29:36.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Turn starboard, 3.6 degrees.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:29:39.861 --> 00:29:41.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:29:41.112 --> 00:29:42.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think we've found it.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:29:42.530 --> 00:29:44.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Maintain course.</i></c.bg_transparent>

448
00:29:44.324 --> 00:29:46.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You should be heading directly</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>toward the cloaking barrier.</i></c.bg_transparent>

449
00:29:48.369 --> 00:29:49.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Power's fluctuating!</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:29:49.704 --> 00:29:51.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:29:56.961 --> 00:29:58.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hull integrity?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:29:58.505 --> 00:30:00.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Some micro-fractures,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but nothing we can't handle.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:30:04.594 --> 00:30:06.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>TUCKER: Switching to backup!</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:30:10.683 --> 00:30:12.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:30:13.937 --> 00:30:15.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trip.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:30:23.446 --> 00:30:25.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's get going with the scans.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:30:27.784 --> 00:30:29.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( buzzing )</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:30:29.536 --> 00:30:30.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>TUCKER: Ah, hell!</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:30:30.870 --> 00:30:32.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there a problem?</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:30:32.372 --> 00:30:34.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The sensor relays were damaged.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:30:35.583 --> 00:30:37.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How much time do you need?</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:30:37.418 --> 00:30:39.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not long,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but we'll have to get back to </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

463
00:30:40.004 --> 00:30:42.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I need to open up the circuit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>housings on the undercarriage--</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:30:42.173 --> 00:30:44.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No way to get to them from the inside.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:30:47.178 --> 00:30:49.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring the descent thrusters online.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:30:52.016 --> 00:30:54.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not planning to land on that thing?</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:30:54.435 --> 00:30:58.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thrusters, Trip,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and get the E.V. suits ready.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:31:09.284 --> 00:31:10.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:31:13.162 --> 00:31:15.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>TUCKER:</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Not exactly my idea of shore leave.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:31:17.041 --> 00:31:20.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: Get to work.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm gonna take a look around.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:31:20.920 --> 00:31:21.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>TUCKER: Don't get lost.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:31:22.005 --> 00:31:23.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:31:36.185 --> 00:31:37.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: How's it coming, Trip?</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:31:38.021 --> 00:31:41.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Almost there, sir. Just two more relays.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:31:42.942 --> 00:31:44.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( electricity crackles )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( yells )</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:31:45.069 --> 00:31:46.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain!</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:31:47.614 --> 00:31:48.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( hissing )</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:31:54.871 --> 00:31:56.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened?</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:31:56.414 --> 00:31:57.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The port thruster ignited.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:31:57.874 --> 00:31:59.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can see that.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:31:59.250 --> 00:32:00.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I was bypassing the last relay,</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:32:00.919 --> 00:32:03.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I must have triggered a surge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the propulsion system.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:32:03.129 --> 00:32:04.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Son of a bitch!</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:32:07.008 --> 00:32:08.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be a long time</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:32:08.676 --> 00:32:11.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>before </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>decides</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to come looking for us.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:32:11.304 --> 00:32:13.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can we launch without a port thruster?</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:32:13.139 --> 00:32:14.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can sure as hell try.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:32:17.435 --> 00:32:19.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: Whoever gets the first clear shot.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:32:22.482 --> 00:32:25.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Careful, sir. That was awfully</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>close to the O2 recycler.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:32:29.948 --> 00:32:32.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I need to spend more time in the armory.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:32:46.589 --> 00:32:48.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( metal screeching )</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:33:02.063 --> 00:33:03.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:33:03.231 --> 00:33:05.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Archer to </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Enterprise.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:33:05.400 --> 00:33:06.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're here, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:33:06.943 --> 00:33:08.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>It was right where you said it was, T'Pol.</i></c.bg_transparent>

496
00:33:09.028 --> 00:33:11.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We got all the scans you asked for.</i></c.bg_transparent>

497
00:33:13.449 --> 00:33:15.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's starlog, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

498
00:33:15.618 --> 00:33:18.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>While T'Pol analyzes the data</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>from the sphere,</i></c.bg_transparent>

499
00:33:18.246 --> 00:33:20.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>we've set a course to pick up Ensign Sato</i></c.bg_transparent>

500
00:33:20.540 --> 00:33:23.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>and find out if the alien</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>learned anything about the Xindi.</i></c.bg_transparent>

501
00:33:26.796 --> 00:33:28.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( knocking on door )</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:33:28.172 --> 00:33:29.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:33:30.967 --> 00:33:34.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I come in? I won't be long.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:33:34.262 --> 00:33:35.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just heard from your captain.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:33:36.389 --> 00:33:39.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>will be here in a few minutes.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:33:39.434 --> 00:33:42.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have learned a great deal</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the Xindi weapon.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:33:42.520 --> 00:33:45.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure he'll find</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the information useful.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:33:45.481 --> 00:33:47.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you for all your help.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:33:49.277 --> 00:33:51.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you given any more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>thought to my offer?</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:33:52.780 --> 00:33:55.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't stay here. You know that.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:33:56.242 --> 00:33:57.535 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:33:58.619 --> 00:34:01.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was foolish to think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it was even a possibility.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:34:02.373 --> 00:34:05.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The next time you invite</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone for a visit,</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:34:05.293 --> 00:34:06.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you might want to let them know</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:34:06.878 --> 00:34:08.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that you're looking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a lifelong companion.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:34:10.423 --> 00:34:11.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't forget.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:34:12.633 --> 00:34:13.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh...</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:34:13.968 --> 00:34:19.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please keep the book</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as a reminder of your time here.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:34:20.141 --> 00:34:21.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was hoping you'd say that.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:34:21.809 --> 00:34:24.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm nearly done,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm anxious to see how it ends.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:34:25.855 --> 00:34:29.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After I've briefed Captain Archer,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll send him to you.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:34:30.359 --> 00:34:32.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was a privilege knowing you.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:34:51.672 --> 00:34:53.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How was your stay?</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:34:53.174 --> 00:34:55.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm eager to get back to </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

525
00:34:55.510 --> 00:34:57.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:34:57.345 --> 00:35:00.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it's any consolation,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your time here was well spent.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:35:01.682 --> 00:35:04.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've learned more about</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Xindi than I expected.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:35:05.186 --> 00:35:08.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And he's offered to keep</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>supplying us with information</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:35:08.439 --> 00:35:11.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for as long as we're in range,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>thanks to you.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:35:11.484 --> 00:35:13.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Glad I could help, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:35:14.946 --> 00:35:17.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There is one condition.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:35:18.241 --> 00:35:21.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He wants you to stay with him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>while he continues his work.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:35:21.869 --> 00:35:24.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I assume you told him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that wouldn't be possible.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:35:25.373 --> 00:35:28.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't order you to do this, Hoshi,</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:35:29.001 --> 00:35:31.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it may be our best chance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of finding the weapon</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:35:31.963 --> 00:35:33.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>before it's too late.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:35:34.048 --> 00:35:38.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With any luck, it'll only take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a few weeks, maybe a month.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:35:40.012 --> 00:35:43.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'd come back for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as soon as the mission's over.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:35:44.517 --> 00:35:47.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't need to tell you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what's at stake, Ensign.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:35:52.400 --> 00:35:55.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll go back to my quarters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and pick up a few things.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:35:56.028 --> 00:35:57.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Hoshi.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:35:57.405 --> 00:35:59.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no reason for you to leave.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:35:59.949 --> 00:36:02.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just give me a list of what you need,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'll have it sent down.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:36:03.202 --> 00:36:06.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I should brief my replacement</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the U.T. upgrades.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:36:06.205 --> 00:36:08.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll take care of it. Don't worry.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:36:08.249 --> 00:36:10.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At least give me a chance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to say goodbye to the crew.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:36:10.710 --> 00:36:12.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish there was time.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:36:12.336 --> 00:36:15.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't take long, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I might not see my friends again.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:36:15.631 --> 00:36:17.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure Travis will understand.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:36:19.468 --> 00:36:20.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Travis?</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:36:21.012 --> 00:36:22.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Travis and the others.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:36:22.805 --> 00:36:24.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They realize how important this is.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:36:25.391 --> 00:36:27.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just thinking about Travis.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:36:29.520 --> 00:36:31.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a regular mind reader.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:36:31.814 --> 00:36:33.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've known each other a long time.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:36:34.442 --> 00:36:36.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is Captain Archer?</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:36:36.819 --> 00:36:40.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be back for you as soon as we can.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:36:40.907 --> 00:36:42.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is he?</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:36:42.158 --> 00:36:43.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hoshi.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:36:43.242 --> 00:36:45.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where is Captain Archer?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Hoshi.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:36:45.953 --> 00:36:48.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open a channel to Ensign Sato.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:36:48.623 --> 00:36:50.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:36:50.583 --> 00:36:52.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our signal's not getting through, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:36:52.919 --> 00:36:55.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's some kind of disruption field.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:36:56.214 --> 00:36:57.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALCOLM: Sir.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:36:57.506 --> 00:36:58.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: What's going on?</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:36:59.008 --> 00:37:00.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My station's down.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:37:02.011 --> 00:37:03.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything's going off-line...</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:37:03.804 --> 00:37:08.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Main and auxiliary power,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>warp engines, life support.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:37:08.935 --> 00:37:10.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( electricity humming )</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:37:11.771 --> 00:37:13.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nice try.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:37:13.105 --> 00:37:16.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What were you planning to tell</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my captain when he got back?</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:37:16.108 --> 00:37:18.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Were you gonna appear as me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and beg him to let you stay?</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:37:18.736 --> 00:37:20.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, you can't do that, can you?</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:37:20.655 --> 00:37:23.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the only one on board</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you can play your tricks with.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:37:23.991 --> 00:37:26.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent> has already returned.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:37:27.036 --> 00:37:28.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their fate is in your hands.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:37:28.913 --> 00:37:30.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is that supposed to mean?</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:37:30.623 --> 00:37:32.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't let you leave, Hoshi.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:37:32.917 --> 00:37:34.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've waited too long to find you.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:37:35.294 --> 00:37:37.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's happened to </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise?</i></c.bg_transparent>

582
00:37:37.296 --> 00:37:40.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you agree to stay,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they won't be harmed.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:37:40.800 --> 00:37:43.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They'll be free to leave orbit.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:37:43.177 --> 00:37:45.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me speak to Captain Archer.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:37:45.388 --> 00:37:46.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not possible.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:37:46.806 --> 00:37:48.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why the hell not?</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:37:49.225 --> 00:37:52.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be happy here, I promise you.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:37:52.311 --> 00:37:54.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why can't I speak to Captain Archer?</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:37:54.981 --> 00:37:57.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no power on your vessel,</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:37:57.900 --> 00:38:01.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and there won't be until</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you agree to remain with me.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:38:02.321 --> 00:38:06.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You would kill over 80 people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to keep me here?</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:38:06.450 --> 00:38:09.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to kill anyone.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:38:09.370 --> 00:38:12.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's why it's essential</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you agree to stay.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:38:18.129 --> 00:38:19.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mustn't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:38:19.422 --> 00:38:20.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( breathing heavily )</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:38:20.673 --> 00:38:21.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's very fragile.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:38:22.258 --> 00:38:24.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm counting on that.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:38:24.135 --> 00:38:26.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now undo whatever you've done to my ship,</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:38:26.595 --> 00:38:29.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>or you will never contact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>anyone again with this thing.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:38:29.390 --> 00:38:31.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>An empty threat, Hoshi.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:38:31.100 --> 00:38:34.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As long as you're with me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I won't need to contact anyone else.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:38:34.228 --> 00:38:37.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As long as I'm with you...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another 60, 70 years?</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:38:37.440 --> 00:38:38.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then what?</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:38:38.691 --> 00:38:41.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What'll you do when</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm grave number five out there?</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:38:41.277 --> 00:38:44.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Without this,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you will never find another companion.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:38:44.905 --> 00:38:47.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You will be alone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the rest of your life.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:38:47.867 --> 00:38:51.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, think of what I can offer you.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:38:51.287 --> 00:38:53.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is your last chance.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:38:59.086 --> 00:39:00.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( electricity humming )</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:39:06.052 --> 00:39:07.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: Report.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:39:07.428 --> 00:39:08.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Power's returning to all systems.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:39:09.013 --> 00:39:10.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Malcolm?</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:39:10.139 --> 00:39:11.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Weapons are coming back online.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:39:12.016 --> 00:39:13.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tactical alert.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:39:13.309 --> 00:39:14.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:39:14.393 --> 00:39:15.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:39:15.728 --> 00:39:16.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's Ensign Sato.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:39:17.021 --> 00:39:18.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put her through.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:39:18.481 --> 00:39:20.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>HOSHI: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain, are you all right?</i></c.bg_transparent>

620
00:39:20.649 --> 00:39:22.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are now. What the hell's going on?</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:39:22.777 --> 00:39:25.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I think it's time to come get me.</i></c.bg_transparent>

622
00:39:25.988 --> 00:39:27.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's starlog, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

623
00:39:27.990 --> 00:39:30.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ensign Sato has returned to </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Enterprise,</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:39:30.326 --> 00:39:32.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>but without any new information</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>on the Xindi.</i></c.bg_transparent>

625
00:39:32.745 --> 00:39:36.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'm hoping T'Pol's analysis of</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the second sphere will bring better news.</i></c.bg_transparent>

626
00:39:37.375 --> 00:39:38.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What have you got?</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:39:38.834 --> 00:39:40.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The data you collected</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>allowed me to create</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:39:40.711 --> 00:39:43.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>a nearly accurate map of the anomalies.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:39:43.214 --> 00:39:44.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nearly?</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:39:44.507 --> 00:39:48.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>These are the coordinates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>where we've encountered strong anomalies.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:39:49.053 --> 00:39:51.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The waves aren't intersecting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>where they're supposed to.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:39:51.138 --> 00:39:54.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The locations are being influenced</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:39:54.100 --> 00:39:56.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>by more than two gravimetric sources.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:39:57.269 --> 00:39:58.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A third sphere?</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:39:58.729 --> 00:40:00.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A third sphere would correct</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>some of the error,</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:40:00.815 --> 00:40:02.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but not all of it.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:40:02.108 --> 00:40:05.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So I had the computer run</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a covariant extrapolation.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:40:16.455 --> 00:40:17.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How many?</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:40:17.915 --> 00:40:20.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll need to get farther</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into the expanse to be certain, but...</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:40:22.211 --> 00:40:23.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At least 50.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:40:25.923 --> 00:40:30.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fifty man-made spheres,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>each one the size of a small moon.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:40:30.344 --> 00:40:34.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And each one generating massive</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>amounts of gravimetric energy.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:40:35.015 --> 00:40:40.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did it ever occur to you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that whoever built these things</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:40:40.438 --> 00:40:43.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>may have done it to create the expanse?</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:40:44.108 --> 00:40:48.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why would someone want to create</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a web of crippling anomalies?</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:40:58.414 --> 00:40:59.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:40:59.707 --> 00:41:01.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did you enjoy the ending?</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:41:01.500 --> 00:41:04.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't do this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want you watching me.</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:41:05.379 --> 00:41:08.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the last time... I promise.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:41:09.467 --> 00:41:13.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've brought you information</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to give to your captain.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:41:13.679 --> 00:41:15.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why now?</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:41:15.139 --> 00:41:19.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're on a dangerous mission.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to see you harmed.</c.bg_transparent>

653
